codex
One relevant caveat surfaced: the UI library has an automatic root resize helper, but the actual 
render call used here is plain `UIManager::Render`, which only renders the current root page. The 
engine-side resize hook still needs `CuiManager::setSize` or equivalent to pack/reflow.
